{"tid":1565062,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"場運動就死嫁啦，再唱果首野，我地就只會變加泰隆","createTime":"2019-09-13T04:01:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-13T04:46:19.000Z","uid":181557,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"9258059366723b5c03eac67f277e3078e018fce2","tid":1565062,"uid":181557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T04:01:33.000Z","msg":"關於所謂高唱香港國歌，是日朋友金句。中國共產黨、香港財閥重新恢復合作，摧毀香港本土運動，期間好多輿論作者、海外學者加入宣傳香港國歌商場大合唱，發過豬頭。<br />\n昨晚IFC商場專門上演所謂香港國歌與中共國歌對唱，要香港人在港獨與中共之間，二者選一，忘記中間漸進可行的香港自治（加強實然主權），美國的香港人權法案一直支持的香港自治。一旦香港人集體進入港獨，美國在目前的一個中國政策的限制下，束手無策，正如美國會放棄支持西班牙的加塔隆尼亞的獨立運動。<br />\n//S Leung： 新一波藉港獨打壓自治運動又黎，偽港獨戲碼又重新上演。大家又再一次忘記梁油民族黨班撚樣點樣係2016搞死成個本土運動。//"},{"pid":"8c93425fa81052101a527724172aec207599cb59","tid":1565062,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T04:02:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"605e70b34ab4fddc21729a9fc132620730d062c3","tid":1565062,"uid":181557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T04:05:20.000Z","msg":"推推推"},{"pid":"1c1d52ab0ed56a3613d670f6293ab3e7f324f2ed","tid":1565062,"uid":181557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T04:46:19.000Z","msg":"推"}]}